snippet.title: Rogue Masters - Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
Find out more about Rogue Masters' gameplay and take a first look at the combat, progression and customization system. 

Rogue Masters is a 6 player co-op horde survival game with souls-like combat and extensive character customization where you fight Entropy in long-lost civilizations. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1063590/Rogue_Masters/ 

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/A5JNTt37Tg

Official Website: http://roguemasters.com/ 

Chapters: 
00:00 Intro 
01:21 Fighting Entropy 
04:13 Strenghten your Willpower 
05:44 Stay tuned
